KGI SECURITIES C said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 28.81% to NT$749,514,000 from NT$1,052,850,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales            749,514         1,052,850   
YOY%             -28.81%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           5,587,735        7,153,492   
YOY%             -21.89% 
=================================================================
 